---
import Container from '../components/Container.astro';
---

<section class="py-16 lg:py-20 bg-soft-cream">
  <Container>
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto bg-pure-cream rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-10 border border-deep-indigo/5 text-center">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-thai-chili-red mb-3">A note from us</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold text-deep-indigo mb-4">
        How to order at Buriram
      </h2>
      <p class="text-dusty-slate leading-relaxed max-w-lg mx-auto">
        Most diners order 3-4 small bowls between 2 people. Mix a salad, a soup, a stir-fry, a grilled. Don't forget rice. Add a Thai milk tea — you'll need it for the spicy ones.
      </p>
    </div>
  </Container>
</section>
